   <body>
      <p>The New Program functionality enables you to create programs.</p>
      <p>You can create a program in the following ways:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>From scratch.</li>
         <li>From other programs (known as Program Template or Program Accelerator) using the cloning functionality. Any program can function as a program template or accelerator.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To create a program from scratch, you can access the New Program functionality in the following ways:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <xref href="creating_programs_from_the_agreement.xml#t255D9F6-BDF2-11F0-1114-09173F13E4C5">Creating a Program from the Agreement</xref>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref href="creating_programs_from_the_customer_incentive_manager.xml#t255EF1E-BDF2-11F0-6087-09173F13E4C5">Creating a Program from the Customer Incentive Manager</xref>
         </li>
      </ul>
